        <NamedIndividual IRI="#Mrugasheersha"/>
        <Literal>To show Women, Cheeks, Way of doing things, To show respect, Scare, Argument, Back Stage, The place of living, Forehead, Meeting of people, Sacred design on the floor, Massaging the feet, Getting people together, House, Holding an umbrella, Stairs, Gait, To call the loved one, To show Movement this hasta is used</Literal>
